nodes.text: Early in the Clone Wars, a mission occurred when Jedi Knight Anakin Skywalker and his Padawan, Ahsoka Tano, set out to return Rotta the Huttlet to his father, Jabba, on Hutt ruled planet of Tatooine.
The two arrived after taking down IG-100 MagnaGuards. Anakin and Ashoka split up where Anikan fought Dooku
